title: Mutts records triple-double in Virginia Tech's 71-59 victory against Syracuse - VT hokiesports.com
content: Mutts records triple-double in Virginia Tech's 71-59 victory against Syracuse  VT hokiesports.com
description: Justyn Mutts showed out with a triple-double with 12 points, 14 rebounds and 11 assists to lead the Virginia Tech men's basketball team over the Syracuse Orange 71-59 at home Saturday.
